## Complete Technical Specifications & Implementation Guide

**Document Type**: Bolt.ai Ready Architecture Specification  
**Company**: SS Garments & Hometextiles by Sri Sai Exports  
**Date**: December 2025  
**Purpose**: Direct implementation guide for Bolt.ai website builder

