## SECTION 1: DESIGN SYSTEM & COLOR TOKENS

### **Primary Color Palette (Global)**

```
FOUNDATIONAL COLORS:
- Warm Taupe: #C4A57B (Primary background, luxury)
- Cream/Off-White: #F5F3EE (Secondary background, clean space)
- Charcoal Grey: #2C3E50 (Text, headers, dark accents)
- Soft Sage: #9CAF88 (Accent, nature-inspired)
- Deep Burgundy: #6B3E3A (Jewel tone, warmth)
- Gold: #D4AF37 (Premium accents, metallic)
- Pale Blue: #B5D6E8 (Organic/soft accent)
- Forest Green: #355C3D (Nature trend, earth tone)
- Mocha Mousse: #8B6F47 (Pantone 2025 trend)
- Navy: #2C4563 (Classic, contemporary)

NEUTRAL GRAYS:
- Light Gray (text secondary): #555555
- Border Gray: #DDDDDD
- Light Gray BG: #F9F9F9
```

---

### **Market-Specific Color Schemas**

#### **UK Market**
```
Primary: Sage Green (#9CAF88)
Secondary: Navy (#2C4563)
Accent: Gold (#D4AF37)
Background: Cream (#F5F3EE)
Text: Charcoal (#2C3E50)

CTA Button Primary: Gold (#D4AF37) text Charcoal
CTA Button Hover: Deep Burgundy (#6B3E3A) text Cream
Links: Sage Green (#9CAF88)
```

