## SECTION 2: TYPOGRAPHY SYSTEM

### **Font Stack**

```
Primary Font (Headings, UI): 
- Font Family: "Inter", "Segoe UI", sans-serif
- Fallback: System fonts

Secondary Font (Body):
- Font Family: "Inter", "Open Sans", sans-serif
- Fallback: System fonts

Monospace (Code, specs):
- Font Family: "Monaco", "Courier New", monospace
```

### **Typography Scale**

```
H1 (Page Headlines):
- Font Size: 48px (desktop) / 32px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 700 (bold)
- Line Height: 1.2
- Letter Spacing: -0.01em
- Color: Charcoal (#2C3E50)

H2 (Section Headers):
- Font Size: 36px (desktop) / 24px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 600 (semibold)
- Line Height: 1.3
- Color: Charcoal (#2C3E50)

H3 (Subsection Headers):
- Font Size: 28px (desktop) / 20px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 600 (semibold)
- Line Height: 1.4
- Color: Charcoal (#2C3E50)

H4 (Card Headers):
- Font Size: 20px (desktop) / 16px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 600
- Line Height: 1.4
- Color: Charcoal (#2C3E50)

Body Text:
- Font Size: 16px (desktop) / 14px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 400
- Line Height: 1.6
- Letter Spacing: 0
- Color: #555555

Small Text (Labels, meta):
- Font Size: 14px (desktop) / 12px (mobile)
- Font Weight: 400
- Line Height: 1.5
- Color: #777777

Button Text:
- Font Size: 16px
- Font Weight: 600
- Line Height: 1.4
- Text Transform: None (natural case)
```

