## SECTION 4: COMPONENT LIBRARY

### **4.1 HEADER COMPONENT**

```
HEADER STRUCTURE:
├── Logo Section (Left)
│   ├── Logo Image (100px width)
│   ├── Company Name: "SS Garments"
│   └── Tagline: "Premium Home Textiles"
├── Navigation Menu (Center)
│   ├── Products (Dropdown)
│   │   ├── Bed Linen
│   │   ├── Bath Linen
│   │   ├── Kitchen Linen
│   │   └── Soft Furnishings
│   ├── Market-Specific (Dynamic)
│   ├── Blog
│   ├── Sustainability
│   └── About
└── Right Section
    ├── Language Selector (Dropdown)
    │   ├── English
    │   ├── Spanish (for Spain)
    │   └── Polish (for Poland)
    └── Contact CTA Button
        └── "Request Quote" / "Contact Us"

MOBILE VERSION:
├── Logo (left)
├── Hamburger Menu (right)
└── Expanded Menu (full-width overlay on click)

STICKY BEHAVIOR:
- Background: Semi-transparent Cream (#F5F3EE with 95% opacity)
- Shadow: Subtle drop shadow
- Remains visible on scroll
- Mobile: Sticky only on desktop view (not mobile)

RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS:
- Desktop: >1024px (full horizontal menu)
- Tablet: 768px-1024px (condensed menu)
- Mobile: <768px (hamburger menu)
```

---

### **4.2 HERO SECTION COMPONENT**

```
STRUCTURE:
├── Background Layer
│   ├── Primary Color (Market-specific, 70% opacity)
│   └── Product Image Overlay (30% opacity, right side)
├── Content Container (left side, 50% width)
│   ├── Headline
│   │   └── Font: H1, Charcoal, dynamic per market
│   ├── Subheadline
│   │   └── Font: H3, #555555, market-specific copy
│   ├── Spacer (20px)
│   ├── Supporting Text
│   │   └── Font: Body, #555555, 2-3 lines max
│   ├── Spacer (30px)
│   └── CTA Buttons (Side-by-side)
│       ├── Primary: "Explore Collections"
│       │   └── Style: Solid background (market primary color)
│       └── Secondary: "Request Quote"
│           └── Style: Outline, border market primary color
└── Right Background Image
    └── Product hero image (high-res, 800x600px)

SIZING:
- Height: 500px (desktop) / 300px (mobile)
- Padding: 60px horizontal (desktop) / 20px (mobile)
- Max-width container: 1400px

RESPONSIVE:
- Mobile: Stack vertically (image on top, content below)
- Tablet: Side-by-side with adjusted proportions
- Desktop: Full hero layout as specified
```

---

### **4.3 PRODUCT CARD COMPONENT**

```
STRUCTURE (for product grid):
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│                                 │
│     [PRODUCT IMAGE 300x400]     │ (Aspect ratio: 3:4)
│     (Hover: Subtle zoom effect)  │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Product Name (H4)               │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Short Description (Small text)   │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Material: 100% Cotton            │
│ GSM: 220-250                    │
│ Size: 68x45cm                   │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ COLORS:                          │
│ [■] [■] [■] [■] (color swatches)│
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ Price: £4.50-5.50 per piece     │
│ (Market-specific currency)       │
├─────────────────────────────────┤
│ [REQUEST QUOTE] [VIEW DETAILS]  │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

CARD STYLING:
- Background: Cream (#F5F3EE)
- Border: 1px solid #DDDDDD
- Border Radius: 8px
- Box Shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)
- Hover: Shadow increases to 0 6px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), slight lift

COLOR SWATCH STYLING:
- Size: 20px x 20px circles
- Border: 1px solid #DDDDDD
- Spacing: 8px between each
- Hover: Outline becomes primary color, cursor pointer

RESPONSIVE:
- Desktop: 4 columns (width: calc(25% - 15px))
- Tablet: 3 columns
- Mobile: 2 columns (1 column on very small)
- Gutter: 20px
```

---

### **4.4 BUTTON COMPONENT LIBRARY**

```
PRIMARY CTA BUTTON (Large)
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
│   REQUEST WHOLESALE QUOTE       │
└─────────────────────────────────┘

Styles:
- Default: Background market-primary color, text Cream, 16px font weight 600
- Hover: Background darker shade (opacity 0.9), cursor pointer
- Active: Border 2px solid market-primary color, background lighter
- Disabled: Opacity 0.5, cursor not-allowed

Sizing:
- Padding: 16px 32px (desktop) / 12px 20px (mobile)
- Min-width: 200px
- Border-radius: 6px
- Transition: all 0.3s ease

SECONDARY CTA BUTTON
Styles:
- Default: Background transparent, border 2px solid market-primary color, text market-primary
- Hover: Background market-primary with 0.1 opacity
- Size: Same as primary

TEXT LINK
Styles:
- Color: Market-primary color
- Text-decoration: none
- Border-bottom: 1px dotted market-primary on hover
- Transition: all 0.2s ease

SMALL BUTTON (for product cards)
- Padding: 8px 16px
- Font-size: 14px
- Min-width: auto
```

---

### **4.5 TRUST SECTION COMPONENT**

```
STRUCTURE:
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                                                          │
│  ✓ 40+ Years    ✓ 100+ Workforce    ✓ 15+ Countries   │
│  Excellence        Skilled             Exported         │
│                                                          │
│  ✓ OEKO-TEX      ✓ GOTS Certified    ✓ Government      │
│  Certified        Organic             Recognized        │
│                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

ITEMS:
- 6 trust indicators (3 rows x 2 columns on desktop)
- Each item: Icon + Text
- Icons: SVG or icon font (20px)
- Text: Body text, Charcoal color

SIZING:
- Max-width: 1200px
- Padding: 40px horizontal (desktop) / 20px (mobile)
- Item spacing: 30px horizontal, 25px vertical
- Background: Transparent
- Border-top/bottom: 1px solid #DDDDDD (optional, subtle separation)

RESPONSIVE:
- Desktop: 3 columns per row
- Tablet: 2 columns per row
- Mobile: 1 column (full width)
```

