### **5.2 DETAILED SECTION SPECIFICATIONS**

#### **5.2.1 Market-Specific Promise Section**

```
LAYOUT: Full-width section with colored background

DESKTOP LAYOUT:
┌──────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Background: Market-primary color (20%)   │
├──────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                          │
│     HEADLINE (Market-specific)           │
│                                          │
│     SUBHEADLINE (Market-specific)        │
│                                          │
│     BODY TEXT (2-3 sentences)            │
│                                          │
│     [REQUEST QUOTE] [LEARN MORE]         │
│                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────┘

CONTENT EXAMPLES:

UK VERSION:
- Headline: "Premium Egyptian Cotton for UK Retail Excellence"
- Body: "Designed for UK retailers seeking contemporary design with luxury quality..."

HK VERSION:
- Headline: "Japandi Minimalist Design Meets Luxury Quality"
- Body: "Perfect for design-conscious HK importers seeking ultra-premium positioning..."

NZ VERSION:
- Headline: "GOTS Certified Organic - Ethical Manufacturing You Can Trust"
- Body: "Our GOTS & OEKO-TEX certified collections feature complete supply chain transparency..."

STYLING:
- Padding: 80px horizontal, 60px vertical (desktop) / 40px/30px (mobile)
- Text align: Center
- Background color: Market-primary color at 10% opacity
- Max-width: 1200px

RESPONSIVE:
- Mobile: Full-width padding, increased top/bottom padding
```

---

#### **5.2.2 Product Categories Grid**

```
STRUCTURE: 4-5 category cards in grid

┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐
│                  │  │                  │  │                  │
│   [Icon/Image]   │  │   [Icon/Image]   │  │   [Icon/Image]   │
│   Bed Linen      │  │   Bath Linen     │  │   Kitchen Linen  │
│                  │  │                  │  │                  │
│   View Products  │  │   View Products  │  │   View Products  │
│   [→]            │  │   [→]            │  │   [→]            │
│                  │  │                  │  │                  │
└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘

┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐
│                  │  │                  │
│   [Icon/Image]   │  │   [Icon/Image]   │
│   Soft           │  │   Ready-Made     │
│   Furnishings    │  │   Garments       │
│                  │  │                  │
│   View Products  │  │   View Products  │
│   [→]            │  │   [→]            │
│                  │  │                  │
└──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘

CARD DETAILS:
- Grid: 3 columns (desktop) / 2 columns (tablet) / 1 column (mobile)
- Width: calc(33.333% - 15px)
- Aspect ratio: 1:1.1
- Background: Cream (#F5F3EE)
- Border: 2px solid market-primary color
- Border-radius: 8px
- Padding: 30px
- Hover: Slight lift (transform: translateY(-4px)), shadow increases
- Image/Icon size: 120x120px (centered)
- Category name: H4, centered below icon
- Link text: "View Products →" with arrow icon

CONTAINER:
- Padding: 60px horizontal, 40px vertical (desktop)
- Max-width: 1200px
- Gutter between cards: 20px
```

