#### **5.2.4 Featured Products Carousel**

```
LAYOUT: Horizontal scrollable carousel (or slider)

[← PREVIOUS]  [Product 1]  [Product 2]  [Product 3]  [Product 4]  [NEXT →]

Each product uses PRODUCT CARD COMPONENT (See 4.3)

CONTAINER:
