### **9.1 REQUEST QUOTE FORM (Complete Specification)**

```
FORM ID: request-wholesale-quote

FIELDS:

1. COMPANY_NAME (required)
   Type: Text input
   Placeholder: "Your Company Name"
   Min length: 3
   Max length: 100
   Validation: Non-empty

2. CONTACT_NAME (required)
   Type: Text input
   Placeholder: "Your Full Name"
   Min length: 3
   Max length: 100

3. EMAIL (required)
   Type: Email input
   Placeholder: "your@email.com"
   Validation: Valid email format

4. PHONE (required)
   Type: Tel input with country code
   Placeholder: "+91 7200033566"
   Formatting: Allow +, -, (), spaces
   Min length: 10

5. COUNTRY (required)
   Type: Dropdown/Select
   Options:
   - United Kingdom
   - Hong Kong
   - New Zealand
   - Poland
   - Spain
   - Other
   Action: Updates form color scheme, currency display

6. PRODUCT_CATEGORY (required)
   Type: Multi-select/Dropdown
   Options:
   - Bed Linen
   - Bath Linen
   - Kitchen Linen
   - Soft Furnishings
   - Ready-Made Garments
   - All Categories

7. ESTIMATED_VOLUME (optional)
   Type: Dropdown
   Options:
   - 0-100 units/month
   - 100-500 units/month
   - 500-1000 units/month
   - 1000+ units/month

8. MESSAGE (optional)
   Type: Textarea
   Placeholder: "Tell us about your specific requirements..."
   Max length: 500
   Rows: 4

BUTTONS:

SUBMIT:
- Label: "SUBMIT INQUIRY" or "REQUEST QUOTE"
- Type: Submit
- Style: Primary CTA (market-primary color)
- Disabled state: Show spinner animation during submission
- Success message: "Thank you! We'll contact you within 24 hours."

RESET:
- Label: "CLEAR"
- Type: Reset
- Style: Secondary
- Hidden initially, shows on desktop

FORM SUBMISSION:

Handler: Formspree / Basin / Netlify Forms
Recipient: office@sstextilehub.com

