## SECTION 10: INTEGRATION POINTS

### **10.1 THIRD-PARTY INTEGRATIONS**

```
1. FORM SUBMISSION:
   - Service: Formspree.io or Basin.io
   - Endpoint: https://formspree.io/f/[FORM_ID]
   - Method: POST
   - Email recipient: office@sstextilehub.com
   - Redirect on success: /thank-you/ or modal

2. GEOLOCATION:
   - Service: MaxMind GeoIP2 (free tier: GeoLite2)
   - API: Fetch via client-side JavaScript
   - Cache: localStorage (1 week)

3. ANALYTICS:
   - Google Analytics 4 (GA4)
   - Event tracking:
     * Page views
     * Button clicks (CTA, product view)
     * Form submissions
     * Market selection
     * Product category view

4. CRM:
   - Service: HubSpot or Pipedrive (optional)
   - Sync: Form submissions → Contact database
   - Tag: market, product category, volume

5. WHATSAPP INTEGRATION:
   - Method: WhatsApp API or Click-to-Chat link
   - Link format: https://wa.me/917200033566?text=Hello
   - Usage: CTA buttons, contact section

6. EMAIL SERVICE:
   - Newsletter: ConvertKit or Mailchimp
   - Subscription form in footer
   - Auto-responder for form submissions

7. SEO & METADATA:
   - Yoast SEO or Moz integration (if on WordPress)
   - Meta tags: Title, description, keywords per page
   - Schema markup: Organization, Product, LocalBusiness
   - Open Graph: Social sharing preview

8. CDN:
   - Service: Cloudflare or similar
   - Purpose: Fast image delivery across 5 markets
   - Auto-optimization: WebP conversion, lazy loading

9. PAYMENT (Future):
   - Gateway: Stripe or PayPal (when accepting deposits)
   - Currency: Multi-currency support (£, €, HK$, NZ$)
```

---

## SECTION 11: SEO META DATA STRUCTURE

### **11.1 META TAGS PER PAGE TYPE**

#### **Homepage**
```
<title>SS Garments & Hometextiles | Premium Home Textiles Manufacturer</title>

